9-cases-in-spore-including-4-linked-to-a-new-cluster-a-private-dinner|archive-date=5 March 2020|url-status=live}}</ref> a boulder+ Gym shop at Aperia, Church of Singapore (Bukit Timah), [[Masjid Al-Muttaqin]], a [[PAP Community Foundation]] centre in Fengshan, [[Dover Court International School]],<ref name=\"SchClusters\">{{cite web|url=https://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/singapore/new-covid-19-cases-pcf-sparkletots-fengshan-mar-25-12574708|title=Singapore reports 73 new COVID-19 cases, new cluster involving PCF Sparkletots centre linked to 18 cases|website=CNA|language=en|access-date=2020-03-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200325143439/https://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/singapore/new-covid-19-cases-pcf-sparkletots-fengshan-mar-25-12574708|archive-date=25 March 2020|url-status=live}}</ref> [[SingPost]] Centre, The Wedding Brocade at Yishun,<ref name=\"TWBcluster\">{{cite web|url=https://www.straitstimes.com/singapore/42-new-coronavirus-patients-in-singapore-3-cases-form-new-cluster-in-yishun-bridal-salon|title=42 new coronavirus cases in S'pore including 24 imported; new cluster at Yishun bridal salon|last1=Yuen|first1=Sin|date=29 March 2020|website=The Straits Times|accessdate=29 March 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200329130533/https://www.straitstimes.com/singapore/42-new-coronavirus-patients-in-singapore-3-cases-form-new-cluster-in-yishun-bridal-salon|archive-date=29 March 2020|url-status=live}}</ref> S11 Dormitory\u200a\u200a@\u200a\u200aPunggol, the Wilby Residences, Hero's,<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.straitstimes.com/singapore/35-new-covid-19-cases-in-spore-3-new-clusters-a-bar-in-circular-road-a-dormitory-at|title=35 new Covid-19 cases in S'pore, 3 new clusters - a bar in Circular Road, a dormitory in Seletar North Link and a serviced apartment in Wilby Road|last1=Yong|first1=Clement|date=30 March 2020|website=The Straits Times|accessdate=30 March 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200331042048/http://www.strai